<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Teacher's Insight: <%= result.fileName %> | CodeDocGen</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet"
        href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/highlight.js/11.9.0/styles/atom-one-dark.min.css">
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/highlight.js/11.9.0/highlight.min.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
    <style>
        .mentor-badge {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d97706, #f59e0b);
            color: white;
            padding: 0.5rem 1.25rem;
            border-radius: 2rem;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .lecture-card {
            background: #fff;
            border-left: 5px solid var(--primary);
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 1.5rem;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }

        code {
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace !important;
            font-size: 0.9rem !important;
        }

        pre {
            background: #282c34 !important;
            padding: 1.5rem !important;
            border-radius: 0 0 1.5rem 1.5rem;
            margin: 0 !important;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <nav class="nav">
        <a href="/" class="nav-brand"><i class="fa-solid fa-graduation-cap"></i> CodeDocGen AI Mentor</a>
        <div class="nav-links">
            <a href="/dashboard">Library</a>
            <a href="/upload">New Intake</a>
            <a href="/logout" class="ms-3 text-secondary">Logout</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container py-5">
        <div class="row g-5">
            <!-- Mentor's Lecture Sidebar -->
            <div class="col-lg-7">
                <div class="mb-4 d-flex align-items-center gap-3">
                    <span class="mentor-badge">Teacher's Insight</span>
                    <h1 class="fw-bold mb-0">
                        <%= result.fileName %>
                    </h1>
                </div>

                <div class="lecture-card mb-5">
                    <h5 class="fw-bold text-dark"><i class="fa-solid fa-book-open-reader me-2 text-primary"></i>
                        Mentor's Session Summary</h5>
                    <p class="text-secondary mb-0 mt-3">
                        Today, we are look at a **<%= result.lang %>** module. Think of this file as a specific chapter
                            in your project's story.
                            We detected **<%= result.metrics.componentCount %> key logic points** that define how this
                                part of the app behaves.
                                Professional code like this relies on modularity—breaking big problems into small,
                                understandable pieces.
                                Let’s walk through what the teacher found in your code below.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <h4 class="fw-bold mb-4"><i class="fa-solid fa-chalkboard-user text-primary me-2"></i> File Walkthrough
                </h4>
                <div class="row g-3">
                    <% result.functions.forEach(f=> { %>
                        <div class="col-12">
                            <div class="glass-card"
                                style="padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 3px solid var(--primary-glow);">
                                <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                                    <div
                                        style="background: var(--primary-glow); color: var(--primary); width: 35px; height: 35px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
                                        <i class="fa-solid fa-lightbulb"></i>
                                    </div>
                                    <h6 class="fw-bold mb-0">
                                        <%= f.name %>
                                    </h6>
                                    <span class="ms-auto text-muted small">Line <%= f.line %></span>
                                </div>
                                <p class="text-secondary small line-height-relaxed">
                                    <%= f.explanation %>
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <% }) %>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- VS Code Style Viewer -->
            <div class="col-lg-5">
                <h4 class="fw-bold mb-4"><i class="fa-solid fa-code text-primary me-2"></i> The Blackboard</h4>
                <div class="editor-shell" style="border-radius: 1.5rem; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid #3e4451;">
                    <div class="editor-header d-flex align-items-center"
                        style="background: #21252b; padding: 1rem 1.5rem;">
                        <div class="d-flex gap-2">
                            <div style="width: 12px; height: 12px; border-radius: 50%; background: #ff5f56;"></div>
                            <div style="width: 12px; height: 12px; border-radius: 50%; background: #ffbd2e;"></div>
                            <div style="width: 12px; height: 12px; border-radius: 50%; background: #27c93f;"></div>
                        </div>
                        <span class="ms-3 small text-muted font-monospace">
                            <%= result.fileName %>
                        </span>
                    </div>
                    <pre><code class="language-<%= result.lang %>"><%= code %></code></pre>
                </div>

                <div class="mt-4">
                    <a href="/download-pdf/<%= result.id %>" class="btn btn-primary w-100 py-3 mb-2"
                        style="border-radius: 1.5rem;">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-file-pdf me-2"></i> Export Academic Report
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>hljs.highlightAll();</script>
</body>

</html>